	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there any way you can confirm the ROM on your cart is the same version as the one you're running on the PowerPak?
<br />
<br />If they used the $0D color black, maybe that has something to do with it.  If so, you could hack the ROM to replace the $0D palette entries with $0F and see if that fixes it.
<br />
<br />I don't know why it would be different on the original cart.  I had often seen glitches when running games on the PowerPak, but it normally only affected a single scanline at a time, and hasn't happened in a predictable way that I've seen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


